One of the errors in the test is error[E0412]: cannot find type PhantomData in this scope. One of the suggested item's in the test output is use serde::__private::PhantomData;, but when I run it locally the suggestion is instead use serde::export::PhantomData;`

I've been having this problem for a while now, but only one machine (win10 19043.1415 w/ vs 2022). Has anybody else had this happen, or is it just me?
Doesn't happen on my windows machine, I'm not running visual studio though
